title: Episode #93 - Brad Williams & ME (w/ a Georgia cameo)
description: Comedian Brad Williams & I hang out in the Mancave & talk about comedy, how Carlos Mencia gave him his start in comedy, & at the end Georgia comes in and meets her first Little Person and learns why she cant say midget.
